      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention DIYers and mechanics! This vehicle is looking for a new home and a little TLC to get back to its best. While it currently needs some significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it serves as a fantastic, budget-friendly foundation for your next project or a great source for parts. Grab a bargain and bring this one back to life!",
