    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been preserved with the utmost care. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine state, still smelling like new with no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively by authorized specialists. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
      "price": 48500.0,
